WEBVTT

1
00:17:13.220 --> 00:17:16.650 
我嫁给你父亲的时候他并不爱我
Your father didn't love me when we married.

2
00:17:16.690 --> 00:17:19.920 
我们几乎不认识彼此
He hardly knew me or I him.

3
00:17:21.090 --> 00:17:25.060 
爱情不是从天而降的
Love didn't just happen to us.

4
00:17:25.090 --> 00:17:27.730 
那是我们这么多年来
We built it slowly over the years,

5
00:17:27.760 --> 00:17:29.800 
从一点一滴中收获的
stone by stone,

6
00:17:29.830 --> 00:17:32.200 
有你一点 有你的兄弟姐妹们一点
for you, for your brothers and sisters,

7
00:17:32.240 --> 00:17:34.800 
有我们每个人一点
for all of us.

8
00:17:34.840 --> 00:17:38.870 
它虽然不像在树林里偷欢那么刺激
It's not as exciting as secret passion in the woods,

9
00:17:38.910 --> 00:17:41.810 
但却更加坚定
but it is stronger.

10
00:17:41.850 --> 00:17:44.710 
更加长远
It lasts longer.

